# =============================================================================
# Pluvicto ctDNA Overlap Analysis
#
# Distinct from scripts 1 & 2. This script focuses on:
#   1. Loading force-called ctDNA mutations at each timepoint (C1, C2, TAN)
#   2. Computing overlap of ctDNA variants with tumour WGS mutations
#   3. Calculating detection rates of site-private (per-metastasis) mutations
#   4. Calculating detection rates of PyClone cluster mutations in ctDNA
#   5. Visualising overlap vs. cellular prevalence coloured by clone identity
#
# Supported patients: 22-049, 22-051
# Timepoints: C1 (cycle 1), C2 (cycle 2), TAN (cfDNA WGS)
# =============================================================================

